						               													<description>SO WHAT ARE THE PULPS?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It&amp;rsquo;s spaceships, jungle lords, and Nazis. Lost cities, underwater adventure, and maybe even a hard-boiled detective or two.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It&amp;rsquo;s about heroes moving from scene to scene at breakneck speed. Hot on the trail or maybe a step in front of the bad guys.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It&amp;rsquo;s clever cliffhangers that leave you wanting more.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;But mostly it&amp;rsquo;s all about the story.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;And that&amp;rsquo;s what drives Larger Than Life. In LTL you step into the story and become a Larger Than Life Hero. LTL moves you from scene to scene each with a different challenge. Complete your challenge and move to the next scene. Fail and you&amp;rsquo;re whisked down another road that leads to who knows where. But if you stick to it and if you&amp;rsquo;re lucky you&amp;rsquo;ll complete all the challenges and that will get you what you wanted from the beginning, a shot at the &amp;ldquo;Big Bad&amp;rdquo;. The Big Bad, the Evil Genius, or the Villain&amp;hellip;we prefer to call him the Yin to your Yang because without the &amp;ldquo;Big Bad&amp;rdquo; there&amp;rsquo;s no story. And it&amp;rsquo;s all about the story. Welcome to the world of....Larger Than Life!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
